<template>
  <el-config-provider :size="size" :z-index="zIndex">
    <HelloWorld msg="Vue.js App With ElementUI-Plus"/>
    <el-row class="mb-4">
      <el-col :span="24">
        <el-space wrap>
          <el-button type="primary">Default</el-button>
          <el-button type="primary" plain>Plain</el-button>
          <el-button type="primary" round>Round</el-button>
          <el-input v-model="input" class="w-50 m-2" placeholder="Please input" clearable />
          <el-tag>Tag 1</el-tag>
          <el-tag class="ml-2" type="success">Tag 2</el-tag>
          <el-tag class="ml-2" type="info">Tag 3</el-tag>
          <el-tag class="ml-2" type="warning">Tag 4</el-tag>
          <el-tag class="ml-2" type="danger">Tag 5</el-tag>
        </el-space>
      </el-col>
    </el-row>

    <el-row class="mb-4">
      <el-col :span="24">
        <el-space wrap>
          <ElementCommonComp />
        </el-space>
      </el-col>
    </el-row>
  </el-config-provider>
</template>

<script>
import HelloWorld from './components/HelloWorld.vue'
import ElementCommonComp from './components/HelloWorld.vue'
import { defineComponent } from 'vue';
import {ElConfigProvider} from 'element-plus'

export default defineComponent ({
  components: {
    ElConfigProvider,
    HelloWorld,
  },
  setup() {
    return {
      zIndex: 3000,
      size: 'normal',
      input: ''
    }
  }
})
</script>

<style>
#app {
  font-family: Avenir, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  text-align: center;
  color: #2c3e50;
  margin-top: 60px;
}
</style>
